description:
The Majestics are Rochester Roots Royalty.  They have been playing reggae since the 70s and still know how to bring it. 

They are one of the bands we let have the stage whenever they ask for it.  You see them once and you know why.  

Their shows are can't miss events, especially when they are thrown here.  

Doors 7
Music 8
$10
name: Majestics at Three Heads
